I follow the release managers. If it's OK for you, please feel free to merge it :) Otherwise, let's merge it in 12.5.

@victorwss Thanks for your feedback. Sadly this particular PR is probably completely unrelated to gradle version + Java issues. 
This PR aims to improve NetBeans' tools cooperation with the gradle module; it never aimed to fix anything between NB gradle module and the gradle daemon itself.

If you can reproduce the defect(s), then great ! Please file JIRA issues for each one separately; if you manage to get a stacktrace of the error, please attach it to that issue. Include reproduction steps; ideally starting from a fresh install or project open. GitHub PRs discussions are not intended for reporting (general) bugs, or for product feedback, the primary purpose is to review and discuss changes proposed in the pull request.
